</title>
<subSubSection id="843EDAA556A1A7F48321830ED2E283B1" pageId="null" pageNumber="349" type="description">
<paragraph id="2EC0810E0750CE06E426458D5E4E4612" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">
Ausdauernd, 80-120 cm hoch, horstbildend. Triebe am Grunde mit braunen Blattschuppen. Alle 
<normalizedToken id="D86A6499F08C56BD773659D62B03DC11" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
flach, 2-7 
<emphasis id="D648CA56631E0DE7A2EFE9B6C37DDCD2" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">mm breit</emphasis>
, wenig rauh, 
<emphasis id="85B07B7CA6B7FDD2F889A4CCB4CCD550" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">mit vorstehenden Rippen</emphasis>
, 
<normalizedToken id="10A97F969859AECE544B9E1123CF7C81" originalValue="grün" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">gruen</normalizedToken>
; 
<normalizedToken id="A4178D6359A94527BBC0EF9426C97F1D" originalValue="Blatthäutchen" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">Blatthaeutchen</normalizedToken>
der obern 
<normalizedToken id="438521023843B1FFBA451B383FDCAC9E" originalValue="Stengelblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">Stengelblaetter</normalizedToken>
ca. 2 mm lang, zerschlitzt; Blattscheiden der sterilen Triebe offen. Rispe meist 10-20 cm lang, nickend, mit glatten, 
<normalizedToken id="39C9985D193387C3C3BD756B8E432F47" originalValue="fadenförmigen" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">fadenfoermigen</normalizedToken>
, nickenden 
<normalizedToken id="20E030E3421DA7309462C5226D6C2149" originalValue="Rispenästen" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">Rispenaesten</normalizedToken>
, die meist erst 
<normalizedToken id="9EB244044EBEE6099C0FAA95424E4150" originalValue="über" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">ueber</normalizedToken>
<pageBreakToken id="3F9FA9FD7ED7050242864C82288CC118" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">der</pageBreakToken>
Mitte 
<normalizedToken id="4B14BCF04DA2C68C398141F10A3F28C9" originalValue="Ährchen" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">Aehrchen</normalizedToken>
tragen. 
<emphasis id="0973104D715DBC6D2088ACCC6E8F123A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">
<normalizedToken id="B614930AF69F6E6575F0FFB2F4620F6F" originalValue="Ährchen" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">Aehrchen</normalizedToken>
8-12 mm lang, gelblich.
</emphasis>
Deckspelzen spitz, nie begrannt, 
<emphasis id="433E7D352870D03C2F77F7E4FFCD67D2" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">mit 5 deutlichen Nerven</emphasis>
(wie 
<taxonomicName id="29361BCE5B5E9A0A5C4CEA399A117810" authority="Nr." authorityName="Nr." class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Festuca" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="null" pageNumber="349" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="paniculata">
<emphasis id="B4EC480B7F12F987E199A067E547689D" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">F. paniculata</emphasis>
, Nr.
</taxonomicName>
3). Vorspelze mit tiefer 
<normalizedToken id="ADCC19638F0C3FB1B9CAAA19CE199F32" originalValue="Längsfurche" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">Laengsfurche</normalizedToken>
(wie 
<taxonomicName id="B5BC2C079893A2311E1D33A1D714C7DE" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Festuca" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="null" pageNumber="349" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="paniculata">
<emphasis id="795DA7A41109E42BA9542A38F2789279" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">F. paniculata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
). - 
<normalizedToken id="A2010C9AA520BE70D17BB41F60A44985" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="7E00B0027EA92B4C0E24C915726737DA" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">
<emphasis id="7F53B9253BF44E509F8F05EDDFE06AA3" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">Zytologische Angaben.</emphasis>
Keine Untersuchungen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="03A5655279088CD83297AC3B1DC0BD8C" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">
<emphasis id="543A511AD81590408C641D71BC0E4720" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">Standort.</emphasis>
Montan und subalpin. 
<normalizedToken id="6F5D887CEBF756EB003306CB62B62BBF" originalValue="Kalkgeröll" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">Kalkgeroell</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="F845297944A92DA3B0B8E1F0719895AD" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">
<emphasis id="9D88770F22F966EE85E46431A2DA1115" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">
Verbreitung. 
<normalizedToken id="619D54B505E0EA624F29F4B24FA0D30A" originalValue="Südostalpen-Pflanze" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">Suedostalpen-Pflanze</normalizedToken>
:
</emphasis>
Vom Comersee 
<normalizedToken id="740344B35953420DC16647FE208282E4" originalValue="ostwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">ostwaerts</normalizedToken>
durch die Bergamasker Alpen bis 
<normalizedToken id="B5052E010B6AA085DF26CDCA0465F57E" originalValue="Kärnten" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">Kaernten</normalizedToken>
(
<normalizedToken id="9142608AB233762EE0E9B3E34176EA33" originalValue="Čavin" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">Cavin</normalizedToken>
und Nanos), in 
<normalizedToken id="9D5688FA398E90CCE284DF8B558441A1" originalValue="Südtirol" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">Suedtirol</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="3D66876EC5EA6C7071E864D123F65688" originalValue="nördlich" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">noerdlich</normalizedToken>
bis auf die Seiser Alm. - Im Gebiet: Grigna, Bergamasker Alpen.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
